# This directory contains benchmark results
# Results are organized by timestamp: results/{YYYYMMDD_HHMMSS}/
#
# Each run produces:
#   - byzantine_detection.json
#   - latency_distribution.json
#   - scalability.json
#   - compression.json
#   - summary.json
#   - environment.json
#
# Example output structure:
#
# results/
#   20260112_143052/
#     byzantine_detection.json
#     latency_distribution.json
#     scalability.json
#     compression.json
#     summary.json
#     environment.json
